@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 - ((tmp + 0.94 - v0 + 0.48) / (tmp + 0.96 / tmp + 0.24)))
    v2 = ((0.74 - (v0 + 0.02 + tmp + 0.95)) + ((tmp + 0.72 / v0 + 0.16) + v0))
    v0 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.41 - tmp + 0.43)) * ((v0 + 0.67 - tmp + 0.19) - (v0 + 0.74 + v2 + 0.50)))
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v1 = 0.84
    data[tid] = v0
